{"tid":999373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國男歌手黃致列吐中國空氣水品質不好被中國網友砲轟 : 韓國人真不要臉 !","createTime":"2019-01-28T15:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T06:37:30.000Z","uid":49388,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f379ab590350111d972b23ce90433fcecf96f448","tid":999373,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"韓國男歌手黃致列，日前在電視節目中，吐槽中國空氣跟水品質不好，播出後被中國網友砲轟，事發後，黃致列在25日發表道歉聲明，說自己想要表達的意思是中國和韓國的氣候不同。<br />\n<br />\n據《觀察者網》報導，黃致列在MBC電視台1月23日播出的綜藝節目《Radio Star》(라디오스타)中，說到了中國長沙，後發現外面什麼都看不見，喝了水後也發現味道不一樣。這樣的吐槽讓中國網友批評「那就滾回韓國阿」、「韓國人真不要臉」、「最討厭這種沒素質的棒子」、「嫌中國不好，那你們別來中國撈錢」。<br />\n<br />\n25日下午，黃致列工作室在《微博》公開道歉聲明，稱因不當言論引起的誤會和不悅向大家誠懇道歉，在節目上想表達的是，雖然中國和韓國的氣候不同，但沒有影響自己參加節目的熱情和效果。不過27日韓國MBN電視台認為黃致列的說法很正常，是中國網友在網路上霸凌他。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190128/640_b2d49bbeca5aee7f9dfe31632412633a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190128%2F640_b2d49bbeca5aee7f9dfe31632412633a.jpg&h=9133f874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自MBC<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20190128/1508968/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190128%2F1508968%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=9Xp0njqz6XOVojkP3vk5m7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=09441f95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190128%2F1508968%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=9aea92bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20190128/1508968/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n2016年1月，黃致列作為首發陣容歌手出演湖南衛視《我是歌手第四季》歌唱競演，在第一期獲得了觀眾票選第二名，第二期獲得第二名，第三期獲得第三名，更於第四期中獲得觀眾票選及歌手互投雙料冠軍的殊榮。"},{"pid":"b9bf2b0f8e7437facc709d293d3ccf5908764820","tid":999373,"uid":10014,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"「嫌中國不好，那你們別來中國撈錢」。<br />\n<br />\n嫌全世界都討厭你，那你們別想著移民外國了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1073a19c34fa2322cdba9d798e796657051e7772","tid":999373,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T16:24:26.000Z","msg":"「那就滾回中國阿」、「中國人真不要臉」、「最討厭這種沒素質的支那」、「嫌X國不好，那你們別來X國撈錢」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba63b2ec610b044f558e93b821af9a7453c6245f","tid":999373,"uid":89530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:12:56.000Z","msg":"講事實都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b256f9ec27b07603c2bd3955938e150632c2c5","tid":999373,"uid":71133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:15:22.000Z","msg":"明明自已都覺得係，但人地講出黎就發爛炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6b566b9cdf84310b5f4128626d67fab8300768","tid":999373,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  d留言"},{"pid":"76986e78f6767854a41a8ce386436054be5e4907","tid":999373,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:19:33.000Z","msg":"有講錯你呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854d8159b4a24a5ee2408556397db1b62f76c4d5","tid":999373,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"玻璃心<i